emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group portrait of groom Milton Jones wearing double breasted suit, and bride Esther Coles Jones wearing suit and corsage, cutting two tiered wedding cake, standing in front of fireplace and landscape patterned wallpaper, another version
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 29, 1955, pg. A17, reads: "Happily Wed - Mr. and Mrs. Milton Jones were married in October. Pictured, the bride, the former Mrs. Esther Coles, helps cut cake. - Harris Photo."
